title: Ep - 17 - Olivia Caridi from Ben Higgin’s season of The Bachelor
description:
Kate asks Olivia Caridi from Ben Higgin’s season of The Bachelor what it was like to be a contestant, quizzes the hilarious writer Brian Moylan about Real Housewives of Beverly Hills, and discusses the season premiere of The Bachelor with Sam Chasse.
